1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,500
Operator told me the GPS failed when the car
went under a tunnel.

2
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:11,000
I gave the bag to Black Box. It said he was wrong.

3
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:18,000
AV labs process hundreds of bags per week.
Nobody reads them end-to-end.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:25,500
Everybody has a theory. Most theories are wrong.

5
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:33,500
One hour of real driving. ROS1 bag. No labels.

6
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:44,100
Operator handed over one sentence: "check the tunnel."

7
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:52,000
Opus 4.7 reads the telemetry. Carrier-phase,
fix quality, relative-position validity.

8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:05,100
Long-horizon agent loop. Native memory.
Streaming events. Source badge: REPLAY — real.

9
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:13,500
Moving-base antenna: clean RTK 94% of the bag.
Rover antenna: never locks. Once. The whole hour.

10
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:24,500
REL_POS_VALID never sets. Dual-antenna heading
pipeline broken before the car left the lot.

11
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:32,000
Operator blamed the tunnel.

12
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:38,500
Black Box: heading subsystem failed at t=0.24s,
forty-three minutes before tunnel entry.
Operator hypothesis REFUTED.

13
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:46,000
This is the fix. Specific RTCM3 message IDs:
1077, 1087, 1097, 1127, 4072.0, 4072.1.

14
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:53,000
Config diff, not a redesign.
Proposed for human review — not auto-applied.

15
00:01:53,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Same single-shot accuracy as 4.6.
Better judgment. More eyes.

16
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:07,000
Abstains 100% on under-specified cases (4.6: 0%).
Better Brier under wrong operator framing.
Reads small text 4.6 downsamples away.

17
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:14,000
Other car runs. A robotic boat.
A clean synthetic bag.

18
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:20,000
Same pipeline. Different robots. Honest verdicts.

19
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:28,000
Same tool, clean bag. Returns nothing anomalous.

20
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:37,500
Will not fabricate a bug. Hypotheses dropped
below evidence threshold. NO_ANOMALY_PATCH.

21
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:45,000
One hour of real driving. Forty-six cents.

22
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:50,000
Benchmark open on GitHub: black-box-bench.

23
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:59,500
Black Box · Forensic copilot for robots
Built with Opus 4.7
